      <div id="res209823347" class="bucketwrap image large" previewTitle="From left, Garrett Berntsen, Jennifer Majer and William Shields compare notes at The Johns Hopkins University School of Advanced International Studies in Washington, D.C. Twenty-somethings have new choices under Obamacare.">
            <div class="imagewrap">
                  <img src="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2013/08/07/studentshealthsegment2_custom-8b320cbc4aa551360bd7809d292585f602b46a7a-s6-c30.jpg" data-original="http://media.npr.org/assets/img/2013/08/07/studentshealthsegment2_custom-8b320cbc4aa551360bd7809d292585f602b46a7a.jpg" class="img lazyOnLoad"  title="From left, Garrett Berntsen, Jennifer Majer and William Shields compare notes at The Johns Hopkins University School of Advanced International Studies in Washington, D.C. Twenty-somethings have new choices under Obamacare." alt="From left, Garrett Berntsen, Jennifer Majer and William Shields compare notes at The Johns Hopkins University School of Advanced International Studies in Washington, D.C. Twenty-somethings have new choices under Obamacare." />         <a href="#" class="enlargebtn" title="Enlarge">Enlarge image</a>         <a href="#" class="enlargebtn enlarge-smallscreen" title="Enlarge">i</a>
      </div>
      
<!-- END CLASS="IMAGEWRAP" -->
      <div class="captionwrap">
                  <div class="caption">
                        <p>From left, Garrett Berntsen, Jennifer Majer and William Shields compare notes at The Johns Hopkins University School of Advanced International Studies in Washington, D.C. Twenty-somethings have new choices under Obamacare.</p>
